{"tid":2342567,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[Chinese]Monster Hunter真人版電影外媒評價極差  IGN：年度最差電影之一","createTime":"2020-12-27T08:34:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T15:27:27.000Z","uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8ea2429847a528dfb9cb0d5fca2f1984c1e5d11d","tid":2342567,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T08:34:39.000Z","msg":"《Monster Hunter》（魔物獵人）真人版電影在本月 18 日正式在美國上映，而外界普遍對其評價頗低，外國評論網站 IGN 直指其是年度最差電影之一。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n《Monster Hunter》真人版電影在 2018 年 5 月宣佈開拍，並由 Milla Jovovich 擔任女主角，當時有指電影預算達六千萬美元（約 4.65 億港元），並會在南非進行攝製工作。而時隔兩年多，該片終於在本月 18 日於美國上映，惟不少媒體均給出低分評價，IGN 更稱其是年度最差電影之一。據 IGN 評論，《Monster Hunter》片長雖然只有一個半小時​​，但就像看了兩倍的時長。即使劇情曲折，亦因缺少一個核心專注點而導致劇情極平淡，而世界觀也沒有任何意義，觀影時給人的感覺像是折磨，故給出 3 分低評價。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n目前《Monster Hunter》電影在 Metacritic&nbsp;上僅獲 42 分，而爛番茄（Rotten Tomatoes）亦根據評論給出 4.50/10 的評分，觀眾投票平均得分則為 3.72／5。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/12/25/monster-hunter-movie/movie-2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F12%2F25%2Fmonster-hunter-movie%2Fmovie-2%2F&d=sZqGLlkYYIxatccyfr7NWKGgm0NOSfkDZSs230CVm%2Fs%3D&h=353fe845\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/12/25/monster-hunter-movie/movie-2/</a>"},{"pid":"ae4e4d306a3c198d14a6f01ac4ad93ab1e125b40","tid":2342567,"uid":284432,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T08:36:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"29a295ff97ad979677e59e5e50086d67d23e26f6","tid":2342567,"uid":180302,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T08:37:55.000Z","msg":"連打手ign 都劣評<br />\nMonster Hunter 應該冇比錢ign"},{"pid":"e03776a4aac012291f0364827e4d3a5acec8f6f3","tid":2342567,"uid":321147,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T08:43:14.000Z","msg":"片長雖然只有一個半小時​​，但就像看了兩倍的時長<br />\n<br />\n即係好抵睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4203bb9d2c04784b83ba46205839ab03969ad12","tid":2342567,"uid"